	   <tr><td colspan=2>This robe simply does not go for this.&nbsp;&nbsp;Depending on where you are, you can get this robe for around 3500pp. If you can somehow make it to Crystal Caverns, bring 2kpp and I can guarantee you will walk out with the robe.  The stats are pretty good considering the looks of the robe too.  Other than the Froglock Bonecasters robe, Robe of melding auras, Tolapumj's Robe and Crimson Robe of Alendine (these are all quite pricey too) it is also really the only robe to wear for mags until they can loot the no drop ones.  The Advisor and Shining Metallic are probably not bad buys either but they just dont look as good with weaker stats for the Advisor and a higher price for the other.  Oh well hope I helped someone.<br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
